%N A248977 Triangle read by rows: T(n,k) is the coefficient A_k in the transformation of 1 + x + x^2 + ... + x^n to the polynomial A_k*(x+3k)^k for 0 <= k <= n.
%C A248977 Consider the transformation 1 + x + x^2 + x^3 + ... + x^n = A_0*(x+0)^0 + A_1*(x+3)^1 + A_2*(x+6)^2 + ... + A_n*(x+3n)^n. This sequence gives A_0, ... A_n as the entries in the n-th row of this triangle, starting at n = 0.
%F A248977 T(n,n-1) = 1 - 3n^2 for n > 0.
%e A248977 1;
%e A248977 -2,       1;
